fields.name: ClusterFlavors
fields.description: The list of cluster flavors under the effect of the filter.

fields.name: ClusterVersions
fields.description: The list of cluster versions affected in Major.Minor format.

fields.name: ComputeIsolationSupported
fields.description: Whether support compute isolation. 'true' means only for ComputeIsolationEnabled, 'false' means only for regular cluster.

fields.name: EspApplied
fields.description: Whether apply for ESP cluster. 'true' means only for ESP, 'false' means only for non-ESP, null or empty string or others mean for both.

fields.name: FilterMode
fields.description: The filtering mode. Effectively this can enabling or disabling the VM sizes in a particular set.

fields.name: NodeTypes
fields.description: The list of node types affected by the filter.

fields.name: OsType
fields.description: The OSType affected, Windows or Linux.

fields.name: Regions
fields.description: The list of regions under the effect of the filter.

fields.name: VMSizes
fields.description: The list of virtual machine sizes to include or exclude.
